{"tid":1476492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動議發起和平理性非暴力鐳射革命 幫警署發光","createTime":"2019-08-15T23:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:01:46.000Z","uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc8a4f38bd0a06b7f4c8301f6a177d362d464da","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:31:17.000Z","msg":"冇非法集結 冇射差佬眼睛 冇衝擊差館<br />\n<br />\n動議大家幫手各區幫警署發光發亮<br />\n每區向警署四面牆射鐳射光<br />\n以此表達對警方嘅不滿<br />\n<br />\n只要各區片地開花<br />\n警署將會係全香港最光猛嘅建築物<br />\n<br />\n報章貼張相出嚟冇示威者衝擊之餘又表達出市民對警察嘅不滿<br />\n完全和平理性非暴力亦唔需要申請不反對通知書<br />\n完全係當區居民自發時間不限<br />\n<br />\n對準政權 鐳射革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28ed4d76961bba7e1cb1e31c49b4c06a2f3fbae","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:31:57.000Z","msg":"對準政權 鐳射革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889b18f50b9bd6008afa65cf60e4515e553a869f","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:32:07.000Z","msg":"對準政權 鐳射革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5e3fe1b56e41de457a9cfe0405b0e1cd2b6f01","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:32:17.000Z","msg":"對準政權 鐳射革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281380f31afb8d11dec368748280c9610a41266c","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:32:27.000Z","msg":"對準政權 鐳射革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4edfb9e988e9b6c20d3e6562ab0004cbbea0575","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:33:12.000Z","msg":"以後大家對邊個單位唔滿意 出動鐳射筆就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2cfe658a9c43019720632bb7071d8d1e3df847","tid":1476492,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,